in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.IFS

Class IFSGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.FractalGenerator
      • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.PixelFractalGenerator
        • in.tamchow.fractal.fractals.IFS.IFSGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Pannable, Zoomable, java.io.Serializable 

    public class IFSGenerator
extends PixelFractalGenerator
    Generates IFS fractals

    Hack to support multithreading:

    Actually makes 2 passes: 1 in single threaded initialization phase without rendering to get starting points for threads (fast) & 1 in multithreaded mode for rendering/animation (slow)
